# Microsoft Purview MCP server credentials (copy to repo root as .env.purview).
# Uses an Entra app registration with client-credentials (application) Graph
# permissions — you may reuse the same app as .env.defender/.env.entra:
#   SecurityAlert.Read.All        (DLP + insider-risk alerts; usually already granted)
#   AuditLogsQuery.Read.All       (Purview unified-audit search) — admin consent required
#   InformationProtectionPolicy.Read.All  (sensitivity labels; Graph beta — name
#                                          verified during live validation)
# DLP / Insider Risk content additionally requires Purview (E5-tier) licensing and
# configured policies; without them the tools return graceful posture findings.
PURVIEW_TENANT_ID=
PURVIEW_CLIENT_ID=
PURVIEW_CLIENT_SECRET=
